high_descs: Go around  and go to the front of the towel holder on the right side of the mirror.
Remove the towel from the holder.
Turn right and go to the right side of the sink.
Place the towel on the sink.
Turn left and go to the front of the towel holder on the left side of the mirror.
Remove the towel from the holder.
Turn right and go back to the right side of the sink.
Place the towel next to the first towel on the sink.
anns.task_desc: Move two towels from the holder to the sink.

high_descs: Turn left for two steps then turn right for three steps, turn right again to face the counter and look up.
Pull the towel from the towel ring.
Bring the towel down and turn right for three steps, turn left for two steps, turn left to face the counter.
Put the towel on the counter, standing up between the right side of the yellow bottle and the front edge.
Turn left for two steps, turn right and go to the wall, turn right and stop at the sink.
Look up and grab the towel from the towel ring.
Bring the towel down and turn right and walk past the counter, turn left for one step then turn left again to face the counter.
Put the towel over the towel already standing on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a white towel over another white towel standing up on the counter.

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the shower, then turn right and begin walking across the room, turn right to face the counter and look up at the wall.
Take the wash cloth off of the metal ring that is on the wall to the right of the mirror.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn left and walk up to the end of the counter.
Put the wash cloth on the end of the counter.
Turn left and walk towards the shower, then turn right and walk over to the wall and turn right.
Pick up the wash cloth off of the metal ring that is on the wall to the left of the mirror.
Turn right and walk over to the end of the counter.
Put the wash cloth on the counter on top of the other wash cloth.
anns.task_desc: Move two wash cloths to the counter.
